== 制作 ==
2011年，{{le|GK Films|GK Films}}取得电影版权，并计划以原创故事重启电影<ref>{{cite web|url=https://thefilmstage.com/news/the-departed-the-town-producer-plans-tomb-raider-reboot-for-2013/|title='The Departed' & 'The Town' Producer Plans 'Tomb Raider' Reboot For 2013|publisher=The Film Stage|accessdate=2017-03-15|archive-date=2018-03-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180318094035/https://thefilmstage.com/news/the-departed-the-town-producer-plans-tomb-raider-reboot-for-2013/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。晶体动力负责人达雷尔·加拉格尔（Darrell Gallagher）向《[[综艺_(杂志)|综艺]]》杂志透露，电影将讲述劳拉年轻时的故事<ref>{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2013/digital/games/tomb-raider-reboot-intros-younger-lara-croft-1200002917/|title='Tomb Raider' Reboot Intros Younger Lara Croft|accessdate=2014-03-26|author=Marc Graser Senior Editor @marcgraser|date=2013-03-04|publisher=Variety.com|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111195602/https://variety.com/2013/digital/games/tomb-raider-reboot-intros-younger-lara-croft-1200002917/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2013年3月，GK Films宣布与米高梅合作制作电影。GK Film创始人{{le|格雷厄姆·金|Graham King}}任监制，第一部电影的开发将立即开始<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=102046|title=MGM Partners with GK Films to Produce Tomb Raider Movie|accessdate=2013-03-27|author=|date=2013-03-27|publisher=comingsoon.net|archive-date=2014-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140703152054/http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=102046|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2013年6月，米高梅选择{{le|玛蒂·纳克森|Marti Noxon}}为电影编写剧本<ref name="TombWriter">{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2013/film/news/buffy-the-vampire-slayer-marti-noxon-tomb-raider-mgm-1200496236/|title=Marti Noxon to Rev Up 'Tomb Raider' Reboot for MGM (EXCLUSIVE)|accessdate=2013-06-12|author=Justin Kroll|date=2013-06-12|publisher=[[綜藝_(雜誌)|Variety]]|archive-date=2013-06-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130615195719/http://variety.com/2013/film/news/buffy-the-vampire-slayer-marti-noxon-tomb-raider-mgm-1200496236/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

