ley-lara-croft-tomb-raider-star-wars-force-awakens-1201717660/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。4月，《[[好莱坞报道|好莱坞报道]]》证实[[艾丽西亚·维坎德|艾丽西亚·维坎德]]已经签约，担任主演<ref name="VikanderCast" />。2016年12月，据报道[[華頓·哥金斯|沃尔顿·戈金斯]]在片中扮演反派。戈金斯称剧情“就像《[[法櫃奇兵|夺宝奇兵]]》碰上了[[约瑟夫·康拉德|约瑟夫·康拉德]]的小说《{{le|胜利：荒岛传奇|Victory (novel)}}》（''Victory: An Island Tal''）。”<ref name="GogginsCast">{{cite news|last1=Kroll|first1=Justin|title=‘Tomb Raider’ Reboot Casts Walton Goggins as Villain Opposite Alicia Vikander (EXCLUSIVE)|url=http://variety.com/2016/film/news/tomb-raider-casts-walton-goggins-villain-alicia-vikander-1201886922/|accessdate=2016-12-08|work=Variety|date=2016-12-07|archive-date=2021-02-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210224074619/https://variety.com/2016/film/news/tomb-raider-casts-walton-goggins-villain-alicia-vikander-1201886922/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Sheridan|first1=Connor|title=Tomb Raider reboot movie is like Raiders of the Lost Ark according to bad guy actor Walton Goggins|url=http://www.gamesradar.com/tomb-raider-reboot-movie-is-like-raiders-of-the-lost-ark-according-to-bad-guy-actor-walton-goggins/|website=gamesradar.com|publisher=Future plc|accessdate=2016-12-20|date=2016-12-13|archive-date=2016-12-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161217110901/http://www.gamesradar.com/tomb-raider-reboot-movie-is-like-raiders-of-the-lost-ark-according-to-bad-guy-actor-walton-goggins/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://collider.com/tomb-raider-movie-walton-goggins-villain/|title=‘Tomb Raider’: Walton Goggins on His “Confused”, “Angry”, and “Desperate” Villain|publisher=Collider|last=Goldberg|first=Matt|date=2016-12-27|accessdate=2017-03-15|archive-date=2018-03-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180318094033/http://collider.com/tomb-raider-movie-walton-goggins-villain/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2017年1月11日，《综艺》报道[[吴彦祖|吴彦祖]]将加盟电影，饰演船长陆仁（Lu Ren），与劳拉共同冒险，努力寻找她的父亲<ref name="WuCast" />。27日，《好莱坞报道》称多米尼克·韦斯特将饰演劳拉的亡父——考古学家理查德·克劳馥勋爵<ref name="WestCast" />。

